               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Terconazole Vaginal Cream 0.4% is available in 45 g tubes with a measured-dose applicator. <content styleCode="bold">Store at 20°-25°C (68°-77°F)</content> [see USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20080825"/>
            </section>
         </component>
